<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fd746c 0%, #ff9068 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 30px; background: #f9f9f9; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    .reason-box { background: #ffebee; border-left: 4px solid #f44336; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Account Deactivated</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Your ChatForge account was deactivated on <strong>{{deactivatedAt}}</strong>.</p>
      
      {{#if reason}}
      <div class="reason-box">
        <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <p>What this means:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>You can no longer access your account</li>
        <li>All your chatbots have been disabled</li>
        <li>You will not be charged for any future payments</li>
      </ul>

      <p>If you believe this was a mistake or would like to reactivate your account, please contact our support team.</p>

      <p>We're sorry to see you go,<br>The ChatForge Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} ChatForge. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</html>